+ Ingest Batch Data\nwith DataFrames
++ spark.read API
+++_ format(): CSV, JSON, Parquet, XML
+++_ option(): header, inferSchema
+++_ load(): path to file / directory
++ File Formats
+++_ CSV / JSON: row-based, flexible
+++_ Parquet: columnar, analytics-optimized
+++_ XML: rowTag option required
-- JDBC (Databases)
---_ format("jdbc") + url + dbtable
---_ Store credentials in Databricks Secrets
---_ Push-down queries via subquery
-- Write Modes
---_ overwrite: replace table
---_ append: add rows
---_ ignore: skip if exists
---_ error: fail if exists (default)
@endmindmap
